			<abstract>
				<p>Testimony of Dwojra Szczuczyńska on the “Hotel Polski affair”, a Gestapo trap resulting in the death of about 3000 Jews who left
					their hiding places on the “Aryan side”, with specific reference to the role of Lolek Skosowski, a Gestapo agent.</p>
			</abstract>
